# Telegram notifications (optional)
# 1. Create a bot: message @BotFather on Telegram, send /newbot
# 2. Copy the token it gives you into TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN
# 3. Start a chat with your bot, then visit:
#    https://api.telegram.org/bot<YOUR_TOKEN>/getUpdates
#    Copy the "id" field from the "chat" object into TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=
